The course gives an overview of main techniques in digital photography. Through practical work we will test out camera settings, picture composition options, post-processing steps, studio setup, working with models and the role of creativity in it.Objectives/eesmärkid:  The goal of the course is to give an overview of technical principles and creative possibilities in Digital Photography to develop the skills of self expression and attentive looking of the World.Learning outcomes/õpiväljund:  After passing the course the student: - understands principles of composition and how cameras work; - is competent with taking pictures with the camera and post-processing images; - knows how to use the photo medium in narrative, representative and creative contexts
